	</div></div><div id="cat_2" class="ui-tabs-panel ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom" style=""><h2>General Questions</h2><br><p><i>Please answer the following general questions as accurately as possible for the best results. You may click on “View Benefit Results” at any time while answering these questions. The more questions you answer, the more likely you are to be eligible for the benefit programs that appear in your results list.</i></p><div id="cat_2_1005" class="ui-question"><div id="qid_1005" class="ui-question-text"><span style="float:left;line-height:25px;"><span style="float:left;"><strong style="float:left;line-height:25px;">1</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What is your race or ethnicity? (Check all that apply.)</span></span></div><button class="ui-clear-question ui-button ui-widget ui-state-default ui-button-text-only" role="button" aria-disabled="false" style="display: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: medium none;"><span class="ui-button-text">Reset Answer(s)</span></button><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="546"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="546" value="ETHNICITY_AFRICAN_AMERICAN">African American</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="34"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="34" value="ETHNICITY_ALASKAN_NATIVE">Alaskan Native</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="35"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="35" value="ETHNICITY_AMERASIAN">Amerasian</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="548"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="548" value="ETHNICITY_ASIAN">Asian</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="37"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="37" value="ETHNICITY_CAUCASIAN">Caucasian</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="38"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="38" value="ETHNICITY_CUBAN">Cuban</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="39"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="39" value="ETHNICITY_HAITIAN">Haitian</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="547"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="547" value="ETHNICITY_HISPANIC">Hispanic</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="36"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="36" value="ETHNICITY_AMERICAN_INDIAN">Native American or American Indian</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="40"><input type="checkbox" name="1005_name" id="40" value="ETHNICITY_PACIFIC_ISLANDER">Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander</label></div></div><div id="cat_2_2081" class="ui-question"><div id="qid_2081" class="ui-question-text"><span style="float:left;line-height:25px;"><span style="float:left;"><strong style="float:left;line-height:25px;">2</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Choose the option that best describes where you live:</span><span class="ui-icon-question-help" id="cat_2_qh_2081"></span></span></div><div title="Question Help Text" id="cat_2_help_2081" class="ui-question-help-content" style="display: none;"><p></p><p>Your response to this question will help us determine if you could get SSI. People who are in a jail or correctional facility cannot get SSI. People who live in a nursing home where Medicaid pays the cost could get SSI if their income is less than $30 per month. </p>
<p> Choose the option that best describes where you live. </p><p></p><span class="ui-icon-help-close"></span></div> <button class="ui-clear-question ui-button ui-widget ui-state-default ui-button-text-only" role="button" aria-disabled="false" style="display: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: medium none;"><span class="ui-button-text">Reset Answer(s)</span></button><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="721" style="max-width: 450px;"><input type="radio" name="2081_name" id="721" value="HOUSING_PRIVATE_RESIDENCE">Private residence</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="722" style="max-width: 450px;"><input type="radio" name="2081_name" id="722" value="HOUSING_NURSING_HOME">Nursing home (cost paid by Medicaid)</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="723" style="max-width: 450px;"><input type="radio" name="2081_name" id="723" value="HOUSING_JAIL">Jail or correctional facility</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="724" style="max-width: 450px;"><input type="radio" name="2081_name" id="724" value="HOUSING_OTHER_FACILITY">Other facility</label></div><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="725" style="max-width: 450px;"><input type="radio" name="2081_name" id="725" value="HOUSING_OTHER">Other</label></div></div><div id="cat_2_1002" class="ui-question"><div id="qid_1002" class="ui-question-text"><span style="float:left;line-height:25px;"><span style="float:left;"><strong style="float:left;line-height:25px;">3</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Which of the following (if any) describe you or your spouse's current and/or past professional experiences? (Check all that apply.)</span></span></div><button class="ui-clear-question ui-button ui-widget ui-state-default ui-button-text-only" role="button" aria-disabled="false" style="display: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: medium none;"><span class="ui-button-text">Reset Answer(s)</span></button><div class="ui-question-answer"><label for="1"><i